This project allow to connect automatically to a proxy and execute the access using user specifyed credentials.
It has been divided in source code putted in the src directory and in bytecode contained in the build directory.
All needed classes/libraries has been included in both directories.
A jar file has been created to overcome to manual compilation of all source code.
There is also a zip file containing all classes and data needed, just unzip and use it.
All data used by AlwaysOnline program is inside the directory data.

AlwaysOnline si executed as a tray icon and provide a menu that allow to specify user credentials, the address of the
proxy and the timeout to use to refresh the authentication.
